#Advanced Rex -- query intended to enumerate and output each raw event to find variations in fields and values used to test the following regex
index=websphere sourcetype=log4j|rex field=source "/appLogs/WebSphereLogs/[redacted]/Log4J_Logs/(?<log>.*)"
|eval raw=_raw
|eval No=1
|accum No
|table No, log, raw

